latestIgtvVideos.title: How to oil your hair without actually using hair oil
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I love experimenting with different hair colours but at the same time i make sure that I take proper care of my hair!!
Since the last 4 months I haven’t been able to do that because salons are shut and hair spas are on pause too😥

So I’ve recently found an alternative for that when i got my hands on the Pantene Open Hair Miracle🥰
I’ve been using it to nourish my hair like oil without actually using oil.
I apply it on my hair from roots to tip for an hour before I wash my hair and trust me it gives your hair a salon like hair spa at home

Make sure you try this once and let me know your experience in the comment section below❤️
#Pantene #AdvancedHairfallSolution
#NoHairfall #PanteneProV #ProVitamin

latestIgtvVideos.title: Here’s how to control hairfall in the lockdown
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So after facing a lot of hair fall and finding out for solutions that’ll help me reduce hair fall, I now have some tips & tricks to share that’ll help you get rid of this too. -It’s recommended to wash your hair 2-3 times a week to maintain hair hygiene and it is also equally important to follow a healthy diet filled with nutrients and vitamins. -Pick a good anti hair fall shampoo and always remember to condition your hair after shampooing them.

As you have seen my earlier posts, I’ve been using the Pantene 2in1 Shampoo + Conditioner for 14 days now and have also included foods filled with vitamins!

Do try these tips out and let me know if this helped you out!❤️
#Pantene #AdvancedHairfallSolution
#NoHairfall #PanteneProV #ProVitamin
Video credits- @_pranavbatra
